nodes.text: The New Jedi Order: Agents of Chaos II: Jedi Eclipse (Talking Book Publishers Inc. audiobook)

The New Jedi Order: Agents of Chaos II: Jedi Eclipse is the unabridged audiobook version of the Star Wars Legends novel of the same name, written by James Luceno. Performed by Chuck Benson, the audiobook was released by Talking Book Publishers Inc. in 2012.
